description:
3D pictures with your phone!

READ THE FULL DESCRIPTION BEFORE PURCHASING.
Support for this application only in english.

Warning: Like any 3D viewing, this application can cause dizziness.
If you have visual related seizures, epilepsy, or other medical condition,
don't use this application.

With Stereo Camera for Pre3, you can generate stereoscopic images with your phone.
Stereoscopy is a method for creating 3D pictures and viewing them without any special gear.

Take your 3D images and show them to your friends, relatives...

Now you can have 3D memories of your favourite places, people, etc... just using your phone.

Enjoy the magic of Stereoscopy!
